divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving east to work at 11:45am. I noticed a strange looking cloud which looked like a ufo cloud. I grabbed my camera and took a few photos. The clouds above looked normal except for this one. It stayed in place with no movement. I did not know what to make of it since it could have been a real cloud. I did notice later that the city was covered with chemtrails.
